graph LR
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]

    %% External Dependencies
    Dashboard -->|runtime| NodeJS[Node.js 22.0.0+]
    Dashboard -->|platform| K8s[Kubernetes 1.25+]
    Dashboard -->|platform| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    Dashboard -->|auth sidecar| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy]
    Dashboard -->|frontend| React[React 18.2.0]
    Dashboard -->|UI components| PatternFly[PatternFly 6.4.0]
    Dashboard -->|backend framework| Fastify[Fastify 4.28.1]
    Dashboard -->|K8s client| K8sClient[kubernetes/client-node 0.12.2]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Core
    Dashboard -->|cluster status| ODHOperator[ODH Operator]
    Dashboard -->|model serving| KServe[KServe]
    Dashboard -->|notebook mgmt| KubeflowNotebooks[Kubeflow Notebooks]
    Dashboard -->|model tracking| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Dashboard -->|metrics| Thanos[Prometheus/Thanos]
    Dashboard -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth]
    Dashboard -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh / Istio]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - ML Tools
    Dashboard -->|feature store| Feast[Feast]
    Dashboard -->|GenAI workloads| LlamaStack[LlamaStack]
    Dashboard -->|NIM serving| NIMServing[NVIDIA NIM]

    %% OpenShift Services
    Dashboard -->|image builds| BuildService[OpenShift Build Service]
    Dashboard -->|image metadata| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry]
    Dashboard -->|routes/ingress| RouteAPI[OpenShift Route API]

    %% Integration Points (Bidirectional)
    DashboardUI[ODH Dashboard UI] -.->|consumed by| Dashboard
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|integrates| Dashboard

    %% Custom Resources
    Dashboard -->|manages| CRs[Custom Resources<br/>OdhApplication<br/>OdhDocument<br/>OdhQuickStart<br/>OdhDashboardConfig]

